name: The name of the Quest.
image: The featured image for the Quest.
release: Array representing the month and year for the release date of the update that added the Quest to the game.
update: The release message for the update that added the Quest to the game.
aka: The alternate name for the Quest.
members: A yes or no value indicating if the content can only be accessed in the game with a paid subscription.
series: The name of the Quest Series that this Quest is a part of, or 'None', if it's not part of a Quest Series.
developer: The name of the Jagex Developer that created the given Quest.
